message.body: Pretty open. Let me know. I'm already at home
Oh shit you don't have to run back out. I thought you were coming from work or something. We can tilt the kilt?
Yeah. Kind of feeling rock bottom? I haven't been to any of those places in a while. Honestly you pick the place and time and I'm there.
I can do rock bottom. Gonna be a one beer queer on you though. I'm being watched like a hawk.
Lets aim for 6. I'll bail a few minutes early
Here having a smoke outside lower entrance
